'''獨立精神獎'''（{{lang-en|'''Independent Spirit Awards'''}}），全称“'''电影独立精神奖'''”（'''Film Independent Spirit Awards'''），成立於1984年<ref name=picker2004>{{Citation |editor=Jason E. Squire |last=Picker |first=David V. |year=2004 |isbn=978-0-7432-1937-2 |oclc=53953524 |title=The movie business book |chapter=The Film Company as Financier-Distributor |accessdate=29 September 2011 |publisher=[[Simon_and_Schuster|Simon and Schuster]] |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=f_ZlSCBuRO4C&lpg=PT145&dq=%22independent%20spirit%20awards%22&pg=PT145#v=onepage&q=%22independent%20spirit%20awards%22&f=false |archive-date=2021-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201152832/https://books.google.com/books?id=f_ZlSCBuRO4C&lpg=PT145&dq=%22independent%20spirit%20awards%22&pg=PT145#v=onepage&q=%22independent%20spirit%20awards%22&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Citation |last=English |first=James F. |year=2008 |title=The Economy of Prestige: Prizes, Awards, and the Circulation of Cultural Value |chapter=The Age of Awards |publisher=[[Harvard_University_Press|Harvard University Press]] |publication-place=United States of America |page=86 |oclc=221175319 |isbn=978-0-674-03043-5 |accessdate=29 September 2011 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=vY3UOFDA2sAC&lpg=PA86&dq=%22independent%20spirit%20awards%22&pg=PA86#v=onepage&q=%22independent%20spirit%20awards%22&f=false |archive-date=2020-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815081747/https://books.google.com/books?id=vY3UOFDA2sAC&lpg=PA86&dq=%22independent%20spirit%20awards%22&pg=PA86#v=onepage&q=%22independent%20spirit%20awards%22&f=false |dead-url=no }}<br>provides alternative start date as 1986, not 1984</ref>，其宗旨是表彰獨立製作的優秀電影作品，於[[美國|美國]][[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[洛杉磯縣|洛杉磯縣]][[聖莫尼卡|聖莫尼卡]]舉辦。一開始稱為'''FINDIE'''獎（或Friends of Independents Awards），自從1999年之後，通常在[[奧斯卡獎|奧斯卡獎]]前一天公布得獎名單<ref>{{Citation |last=Steele |first=Bruce C. |publication-date=28 February 2006 |title=It's Ang Lee vs. Gregg Araki! |magazine=[[The_Advocate|The Advocate]] |publisher=[[Here_Media|Here Media]] |page=49 |accessdate=28 September 2011 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=5GQEAAAAMBAJ&lpg=PA49&dq=%22independent%20spirit%20awards%22&pg=PA49#v=onepage&q=%22independent%20spirit%20awards%22&f=false |archive-date=2017-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301001632/https://books.google.com/books?id=5GQEAAAAMBAJ&lpg=PA49&dq=%22independent%20spirit%20awards%22&pg=PA49#v=onepage&q=%22independent%20spirit%20awards%22&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 对象 ==
獨立精神獎主要表揚那些在[[专制|专制]]国家中不受[[独裁|独裁]]政府干预，拍摄与官方意识形态不符的影片。

